16
00:00:41.910 --> 00:00:44.130
Following the financial crisis,

17
00:00:44.130 --> 00:00:46.415
there has been
quite substantial regulation

18
00:00:46.415 --> 00:00:47.870
of both debit and

19
00:00:47.870 --> 00:00:51.740
credit cards along the lines
