63
00:02:44.665 --> 00:02:49.890
Then you go to let's say
IKEA to buy a $100 couch.

64
00:02:49.890 --> 00:02:51.180
Well, by the time you're IKEA

65
00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:53.279
transaction has been processed,

66
00:02:53.279 --> 00:02:55.575
you've overdrawn your account,

67
00:02:55.575 --> 00:02:57.080
which means you're liable for

68
00:02:57.080 --> 00:03:00.565
an overdraft fee for
your IKEA transaction.

69
00:03:00.565 --> 00:03:02.150
What banks did though and were

70
00:03:02.150 --> 00:03:03.980
able to do since we did not

71
00:03:03.980 --> 00:03:05.150
have and still do not have

72
00:03:05.150 --> 00:03:07.445
a real-time payment
structure in this country,

73
