79
00:03:22.820 --> 00:03:25.340
now thanks to the processing
order that the bank has

80
00:03:25.340 --> 00:03:28.745
selected has become two
expensive overdrafts.

81
00:03:28.745 --> 00:03:31.340
Practices like these
resulted in overdraft

82
00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:33.980
being a very significant
source of revenue for

83
00:03:33.980 --> 00:03:37.970
financial institutions and
one they relied on with

84
00:03:37.970 --> 00:03:43.045
the great success for their
debit card using customers.

85
00:03:43.045 --> 00:03:44.820
In the aftermath of the crisis,

86
00:03:44.820 --> 00:03:47.315
popular attention
focused significantly

87
00:03:47.315 --> 00:03:50.525
