88
00:03:50.525 --> 00:03:52.850
There were a series of
New York Times articles

89
00:03:52.850 --> 00:03:54.590
that lamented the
fact that consumers

90
00:03:54.590 --> 00:03:56.480
would regularly pay $40 for

91
00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:58.975
their morning latte
