a $35 overdraft fee

93
00:04:01.515 --> 00:04:04.220
attached to their
$5 debit purchase.

94
00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:06.200
This is again especially

95
00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:08.960
troubling as
a distributional matter.

96
00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:12.650
Only 10 percent of consumers
are responsible for

97
00:04:12.650 --> 00:04:17.000
around 85 percent of overdraft
revenue that's generated.

98
00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:20.490
This means that, there are
frequent overdrafters,

99
00:04:20.490 --> 00:04:23.055
those who overdraft
with great regularity,

100
00:04:23.055 --> 00:04:25.520
tend to subsidize
the existence of things

101
