when they overdraw

123
00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:27.650
their accounts either
by transacting,

124
00:05:27.650 --> 00:05:29.690
or by withdrawing
money from the ATM,

125
00:05:29.690 --> 00:05:33.310
that they don't actually have
sufficient funds to cover.

126
00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:35.630
In the aftermath of
the crisis before

127
00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:38.810
the banks are able to levy
these overdraft fees,

128
00:05:38.810 --> 00:05:41.014
consumers are now
required to affirmatively

129
00:05:41.014 --> 00:05:43.910
opt in to banks
overdraft protection..

130
00:05:43.910 --> 00:05:46.850
This has reduced the share
of customers that are even

131
00:05:46.850 --> 00:05:50.610
capable of incurring overdraft
fees from 100 percent,

132
00:05:50.610 --> 00:05:53.249
so essentially all of
US bank customers,

133
00:05:53.249 --> 00:05:56.355
to around 15 percent
of customers,

134
00:05:56.355 --> 00:05:58.280
and decreased overdraft revenues

135
00:05:58.280 --> 00:06:01.840
substantially for
financial institutions.

136
00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:04.160
The largest financial
institutions

137
00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:05.720
who realized that overdraft is

138
00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:08.150
a notorious product and
that these practices are

139
00:06:08.150 --> 00:06:11.165
frowned upon by their customers
and much more broadly,

140
00:06:11.165 --> 00:06:14.990
responded to this regulation
by embracing it and even

141
00:06:14.990 --> 00:06:18.900
going beyond the requirements
of the new default rules.

142
00:06:18.900 --> 00:06:23.270
In some instances, by
eliminating overdraft entirely

143
00:06:23.270 --> 00:06:27.710
as a product and no longer
charging consumers high costs,

144
00:06:27.710 --> 00:06:31.460
instead declining these
transactions if they occur.

145
00:06:31.460 --> 00:06:35.285
Some banks offer instead
for consumers the ability

146
00:06:35.285 --> 00:06:39.085
to rewind expensive overdrafts,

147
00:06:39.085 --> 00:06:42.860
not charging consumers
a high overdraft fee if they're

148
00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:46.930
able to replenish
their accounts within 24 hours,

149
00:06:46.930 --> 00:06:50.710
