banks overdraft protection,

160
00:07:16.010 --> 00:07:18.060
they are disproportionately
the low-income,

161
00:07:18.060 --> 00:07:20.510
less financially
sophisticated consumers,

162
00:07:20.510 --> 00:07:21.590
who tended to generate

163
00:07:21.590 --> 00:07:24.880
